{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a7e07c708b","title":"关于反“扫荡”等问题给李井泉等的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2eb8e9c39c","index":0,"year":1939,"month":7,"day":3,"articleId":"a7e07c708b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ba464cc7f3","type":"paragraph","text":"关于反“扫荡”等问题给李井泉等的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a7e07c708b"},{"id":"db29fbdac0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年7月3日）中国抗战已进入第二阶段，目前故人在其占领区内的“扫荡必较前加紧，我们在敌后反“扫荡”的任务也必然更加繁重和困难。因此必须加强我军的党的领导和政治工作，巩固党的组织，巩固部队的组织，加强部队的战斗力，并乘绥东专员已逃的时机，大方建立当地抗日政权的工作，争取自卫军配合我军坚持抗日[1]这是毛泽东和王祥、代远关于反“扫荡”等问题给李井泉、姚请等的指示。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a7e07c708b"}],"page":{"id":"838e742f82","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"a7e07c708b","start":476,"end":476}}}},"__N_SSG":true}